desc: GLOBEPADDLER - your european kayakshop for the best kayak and canoe equipment you can get! Whitewater - Touring - Seakayaking - Rafting. We've got it all: boats, ISUP paddleboards, safety gear, cags, suits, pfds, spraydecks, helmets, paddles and more for your spirit of watersports. Pushing your world of kayaking!
